    <h5>
     <img alt="Undergraduate student Sergio" class="img_L" height="90" src="/images/sergio_90.jpg" width="90"/>
     <a href="https://news.ucr.edu/articles/2018/12/12/physics-undergraduate-student-headed-cern" target="_blank">
      UCR physics undergraduate student headed to CERN
     </a>
    </h5>
    <p>
     <span>
      <span>
       Sergio Garcia has an extraordinary opportunity to do hands-on work in one of the most famous centers for scientific research in the world. He
      </span>
      will do research during the winter quarter on a particle detector at the Large Hadron Collider, the world's largest and most powerful particle accelerator.
     </span>
    </p>
